Feature	DevOps	DevSecOps
Focus	Speed of development and deployment	Security integrated in development
Security	Considered at the end (reactive)	Embedded from the start (proactive)
Tools	CI/CD pipelines, automation tools	Security scanning, vulnerability tools
Responsibility	Dev and Ops teams	Everyone (Dev, Ops, and Security teams)
Goal	Faster release cycles	Secure and compliant software delivery
